1. Add input validation using `express-validator`.
2. Implement authentication and authorization if routes become private.
3. Add security headers using `helmet`.
4. Add rate limiting using `express-rate-limit`.
5. Add CORS policy configuration using `cors`.
6. Set up proper error handling.
