If the app is exposed over the internet, ensure it uses HTTPS (TLS) to encrypt traffic.

#### ✳️ Recommendation:
Serve the app over HTTPS (especially for endpoints requiring authentication). If you're deploying, always enable TLS through your hosting provider or use reverse proxy services like NGINX or Cloudflare to enforce HTTPS.

